{"data":[{"date":"15:46 22/06","title":"C\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chi 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua \"trai \u0111\u1eb9p\" tuy\u1ec3n Nga","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/co-doi-bong-chi-25-trieu-bang-mua-trai-dep-tuyen-nga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Aleksandr Golovin c\u1ee7a CSKA Moscow b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin s\u1eafp g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ee9 2 cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">CSKA Moscow t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Golovin cho Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Aleksandr Golovin l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh CSKA Moscow. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng, ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Aleksandr Golovin \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Aleksandr Golovin \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/co-doi-bong-chi-25-trieu-bang-mua-trai-dep-tuyen-nga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>CSKA Moscow t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Alex Golovin cho Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed1c \u0111\u00f4, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i v\u00e0 t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996. V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CSKA Moscow, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAleksandr Golovin \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Nga \u1edf World Cup 2018, trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u1ea2 R\u1eadp X\u00ea \u00dat v\u00e0 Ai C\u1eadp Golovin \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 2 tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n gi\u00fap anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Golovin, M.U c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Juventus m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, tuy nhi\u00ean <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-italia/cska-tu-choi-ban-golovin-cho-juventus-176-188909.html\" target=\"_blank\">CSKA Moscow t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Golovin cho Juventus</span> v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Golovin l\u00ean 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Aleksandr Golovin c\u1ee7a CSKA Moscow b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin s\u1eafp g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ee9 2 cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho khen ngoi Golovin\" title=\"Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i Golovin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Nga-vs-Saudi-Arabia-bang-A-World-Cup-2018-Tuyet-voi-Golovin-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Golovin l\u00ean 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Italia s\u1ebd n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga l\u00ean 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Juventus c\u00f2n tr\u1ea3 th\u00eam 5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n nhanh ch\u00f3ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Tuttosport, CSKA Moscow \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, vi\u1ec7c Golovin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"465","checkdouble":"189263"},{"date":"15:46 22/06","title":"Chelsea gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 b\u1eb1ng \"h\u00e0ng hot\" Seria A","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/4/8/trung-ve-phil-jones-hinh-anh-3.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c gi\u00fap CLB AS Roma v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League, trung v\u1ec7 Kostas Manolas \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London, Chelsea.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>Chelsea gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 b\u1eb1ng Kostas Manolas</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. N\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y Chelsea c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t m\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chinh ph\u1ee5c c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u. V\u00e0 theo ngu\u1ed3n tin m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, CLB Chelsea c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hy L\u1ea1p Kostas Manolas v\u1edbi CLB AS Roma.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kostas Manolas t\u1eeb AS Roma h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kostas Manolas t\u1eeb AS Roma h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/1/11/Chelsea-muon-co-Kostas-Manolas-tu-AS-Roma-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kostas Manolas t\u1eeb AS Roma</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 26, Kostas Manolas \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 - m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, nhanh nh\u1eb9n, d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 tinh qu\u00e1i. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hy L\u1ea1p \u0111ang l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh n\u01a1i trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Olimpico v\u00e0 gi\u00fap CLB n\u00e0y l\u1eadp&nbsp;chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u khi l\u1ecdt t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18. Manolas c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Barca \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1eeba qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, BL\u0110 Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u01b0a Manolas v\u1ec1 Stamford Bridge. M\u1ee9c ph\u00ed c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 trong kho\u1ea3ng 36-38 tri\u1ec7u euro.&nbsp;Chelsea c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng 5 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a cho Manolas.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i Manolas, Chelsea c\u0169ng s\u1eafp ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trung v\u1ec7 Daniele Rugani t\u1eeb Juventus. S\u1edf d\u0129 The Blues \u01b0a d\u00f9ng c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Serie A b\u1edfi HLV Maurizio Sarri s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m t\u00e2n HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea v\u00e0 \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1edbi nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u00e0 \u00f4ng bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Maurizio Sarri c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, BL\u0110 Chelsea c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng &ldquo;gi\u1ea3i ng\u00e2n&rdquo; h\u00e0ng tr\u0103m tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-co-tan-binh-dau-tien-voi-gia-31-trieu-bang-172-189240.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/21/chelsea-co-tan-binh-dau-tien-voi-gia-31-trieu-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-co-tan-binh-dau-tien-voi-gia-31-trieu-bang-172-189240.html\">Chelsea c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng?</span><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 v\u1edbi...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/loftuscheek-ra-loi-canh-cao-chelsea-172-189132.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/loftuscheek-ra-loi-canh-cao-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/loftuscheek-ra-loi-canh-cao-chelsea-172-189132.html\">Sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o t\u1edbi CLB Chelsea</span><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh Ruben Loftus-Cheek m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o CLB Chelsea v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-fabregas-172-189078.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/23/chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-fabregas.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-fabregas-172-189078.html\">Chelsea chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Fabregas</span><br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Miralem Pjanic thay Cesc Fabregas, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"464","checkdouble":"189265"},{"date":"15:43 22/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Brazil vs Costa Rica 19h00 ng\u00e0y 22/6 (World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/link-xem-brazil-vs-costa-rica.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 15 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u HAGL Ho\u00e0ng Anh Gia Lai vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 22/6.</h2>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n: 2-1<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n: Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng (3'); C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng (10'); Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng (41')<hr>\r\n<br>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i kh\u00e1 cay \u0111\u1eafng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, HAGL b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t cao trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Tuy nhi\u00ean tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u1ecb d\u1ed9i g\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1nh khi chuy\u00ean gia t\u1ea1o si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m Nguy\u1ec5n Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m HAGL khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ee9ng ch\u00f4n ch\u00e2n nh\u00ecn b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Minh Vuong ghi ban tran Da Nang vs HAGL\" title=\"Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1eadn \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Da-Nang-2-1-HAGL-Chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng ghi b\u00e0n gi\u00fap HAGL t\u1ea1m d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n thua s\u1edbm khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 sau \u0111\u00f3 \u00edt ph\u00fat, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m. Tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t, s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap HAGL d\u1ec5 \u0111\u00e1 h\u01a1n. Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c uy hi\u1ebfp khung th\u00e0nh S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC. Tuy nhi\u00ean trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao b\u00ean ph\u00eda &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m k\u00e9m ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, nh\u1eefng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n Thanh, Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7p 1 s\u1ebd kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a th\u00ec \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 41, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u1ede t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao 1m65 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">2-1 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 sau 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 1. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1m ngh\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"463","checkdouble":"189267"},{"date":"16:09 22/06","title":"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua sao M.U sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Iniesta","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/8/barca-muon-mua-sao-mu-sau-su-ra-di-cua-iniesta.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, HLV Ernesto Valverde c\u1ee7a Barca \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn Paul Pogba l\u00e0m ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Iniesta \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</h2><h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Pogba \u0111\u1ec3 thay Iniesta</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Andres Iniesta \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay CLB Barcelona \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>S\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a I8 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7t ra nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi BHL Barca c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n HLV Ernesto Valverde trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ra ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a anh.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paul Pogba cua M.U\" title=\"Paul Pogba cua M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-225-juve-tinh-gay-soc-voi-pogba.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a M.U</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 theo t\u1edd Don Balon th\u00ec&nbsp; \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi Paul Pogba, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e0 HLV Valverde tin t\u01b0\u1edfng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eadp nh\u1ea3, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt t\u1ea1i Nou Camp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Pogba ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n khi m\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1ea1i Man Utd trong hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 t\u1eeb T\u00e2y Ban Nha, anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd nh\u1eb1m &lsquo;\u0111\u1ed5i gi\u00f3&rsquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1i kh\u00f3 \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 M.U s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n r\u1ebb ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Theo t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u, con s\u1ed1 m\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 mua Pogba t\u1eeb Juventus v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 105 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Barca, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Pogba, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo s\u00e1t Miralem Pjanic c\u1ee7a Juventus v\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang l\u00ean c\u1ee7a Tottenham, Christian Eriksen. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n 2 c\u1ee7a Blaugrana n\u1ebfu v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Pogba th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-muon-gay-soc-voi-sao-khung-barca-172-189262.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/tottenham-muon-gay-soc-voi-sao-khung-barca.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-muon-gay-soc-voi-sao-khung-barca-172-189262.html\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi sao kh\u1ee7ng Barca</span><br>\r\nTottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Jordi Alba c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, Spurs c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi t\u1edbi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-nham-nguoi-cu-barca-nang-cap-tuyen-giua-180-189259.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/23/real-madrid-nham-nguoi-cu-barca-nang-cap-tuyen-giua.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-nham-nguoi-cu-barca-nang-cap-tuyen-giua-180-189259.html\">Real Madrid nh\u1eafm ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Barca n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa</span><br>\r\nReal Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Thiago Alcantara c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Mateo Kovacic ra \u0111i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Marca c\u1ee7a TBN \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-ra-gia-pjanic-it-nhat-80-trieu-euro-176-189062.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/7/13/miralem-pjanic-juventus-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-ra-gia-pjanic-it-nhat-80-trieu-euro-176-189062.html\">Juventus b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t cho Real v\u00e0 Barca</span><br>\r\nJuventus ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Pjanic l\u00ean t\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro. H\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ec1n h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 khi m\u00e0 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m n\u00e0y bao g\u1ed3m Real...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"462","checkdouble":"189268"},{"date":"16:02 22/06","title":"3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Peru","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/3-ly-do-giup-dt-phap-nhe-nhang-vuot-qua-peru.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Australia, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Les Bleus gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n c\u00f9ng su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C.</h2><h2>Nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Deschamps</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n thi\u1ebfu \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc Australia, HLV Didier Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Peru.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDeschamps \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. V\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Peru h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Peru h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/155653-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Deschamps c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Peru</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDeschamps ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 gi\u1ed1ng tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Australia. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ch\u00fat \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00e1c. Olivier Giroud \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 chia l\u1eeda ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi Antoine Griezmann tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBlaise Matuidi c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 thay cho Corentin Tolisso. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a Kante v\u00e0 Matuidi, Pogba \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i t\u1ef1 do h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n khi Ph\u00e1p ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 m\u1ea1ch l\u1ea1c h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n. \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00eam qua c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p l\u00fac n\u00e0y. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ea1m t\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng n\u0103m nay, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn &ldquo;G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng G\u00f4-loa&rdquo; s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<h2>C\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 th\u00e9p Umtiti &ndash; Varane</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-phap-vs-peru-463-189178.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru</span>. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 t\u1ecf ra thua k\u00e9m ch\u00fat n\u00e0o, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u1ec1 kh\u00e2u t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ea3 hai hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng t\u00e1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n b\u00e0n. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i Umtiti v\u00e0 Varane \u0111\u00e3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn binh Inca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng nhau c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 8 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u00f3 3 ph\u00e1 t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Peru t\u1ea1o s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Umtiti v\u00e0 Varane c\u0169ng t\u1ea1o ra t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 64 pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 94 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nUmtiti v\u00e0 Varane \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a h\u1eb3n l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 d\u1ea1n d\u00e0y kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong v\u00f2ng 1 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<h2>Kylian Mbappe t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe\" title=\"Mbappe\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Nhung-diem-nhan-Phap-vs-Peru-1-0-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mbappe c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u0103ng hoa tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mbappe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 vi\u00ean ng\u1ecdc qu\u00fd ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. V\u00e0 sao tr\u1ebb 19 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111ang b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00eam qua, Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 c\u0169ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i teen n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t. Nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng r\u00ea d\u1eaft kh\u00f3 n\u1eafm b\u1eaft c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y li\u00ean t\u1ee5c khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Peru ph\u1ea3i ch\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea, Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra 4 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng r\u00ea b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00eam qua, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Mbappe c\u00f2n tung ra 2 c\u00fa s\u00fat, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111i tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch. Anh ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng 49 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u1ee9c 84%.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Ph\u00e1p g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf kh\u00f3a c\u00e1c h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd, Mbappe b\u1ed7ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh h\u1ea1t nh\u00e2n quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Les Bleus. V\u1edbi \u0111\u00e0 n\u00e0y, Mbappe th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1eaft x\u00edch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Peru:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-cua-phap-truoc-peru-421-189255.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/pogba-ca-ngoi-kante-sau-tran-thang-truoc-peru-421-189243.html\">Pogba ca ng\u1ee3i Kante sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"461","checkdouble":"189269"},{"date":"17:52 22/06","title":"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/ket-qua-hagl-vs-sai-gon-tran-dau-vong-15-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 15 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u HAGL Ho\u00e0ng Anh Gia Lai vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 22/6.</h2>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n: 2-1<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n: Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng (3'); C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng (10'); Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng (41')<hr>\r\n<br>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i kh\u00e1 cay \u0111\u1eafng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, HAGL b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t cao trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Tuy nhi\u00ean tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u1ecb d\u1ed9i g\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1nh khi chuy\u00ean gia t\u1ea1o si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m Nguy\u1ec5n Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m HAGL khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ee9ng ch\u00f4n ch\u00e2n nh\u00ecn b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Minh Vuong ghi ban tran Da Nang vs HAGL\" title=\"Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1eadn \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Da-Nang-2-1-HAGL-Chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng ghi b\u00e0n gi\u00fap HAGL t\u1ea1m d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n thua s\u1edbm khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 sau \u0111\u00f3 \u00edt ph\u00fat, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m. Tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t, s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap HAGL d\u1ec5 \u0111\u00e1 h\u01a1n. Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c uy hi\u1ebfp khung th\u00e0nh S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC. Tuy nhi\u00ean trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao b\u00ean ph\u00eda &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m k\u00e9m ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, nh\u1eefng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n Thanh, Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7p 1 s\u1ebd kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a th\u00ec \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 41, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u1ede t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao 1m65 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">2-1 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 sau 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 1. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1m ngh\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"460","checkdouble":"189270"},{"date":"16:19 22/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ea3m cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Nigeria vs Iceland","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nhan-dinh-nigeria-vs-iceland-va-du-doan-iceland-vs-nigeria.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Iceland \u0111ang n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018. V\u00e0 m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m, ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c mang l\u1ea1i cho ch\u00fang ta m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>\u00cdt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (t\u1ed1i \u0111a 2 b\u00e0n)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: <strong>H\u00f2a 0-0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1:</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<em>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u:</em> Nigeria vs Iceland<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1eddi gian: </em>22h ng\u00e0y 22/6<br>\r\n<em>\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m:</em> S\u00e2n Volgograd Arena (Volgograd)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>TLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>Nigeria 0.97*0:0*0.98 Iceland<br>\r\n<em>TBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn:</em> Nhi\u1ec1u -0.97*2*0.90 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Iceland 22h ng\u00e0y 226 v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Bongda24h h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Iceland 22h ng\u00e0y 226 v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Bongda24h h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/nhan-dinh-nigeria-vs-iceland-va-du-doan-iceland-vs-nigeria.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Iceland 22h ng\u00e0y 22/6</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nKhan hi\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng (U 2)</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nIceland \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng khi c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Argentina 1-1 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018. B\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ea3o \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00f9i s\u00e2u, t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh ph\u00f2ng tuy\u1ebfn v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn Lionel Messi c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i \u00f4m h\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPhong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Iceland \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 xa l\u1ea1 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ai \u0111\u00e3 theo d\u00f5i h\u1ecd \u1edf Euro 2016. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh Strakarnir okkar \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e9p k\u00edn m\u1ecdi kh\u00f4ng gian d\u00e0nh cho Argentina.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Iceland phong ngu chat che\" title=\"Iceland phong ngu chat che\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Iceland-phong-ngu-chat-che.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Iceland ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t k\u00edn k\u1ebd</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChung cu\u1ed9c, d\u00f9 ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c \u00e9p, ch\u1ecbu c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty, Iceland v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00f4ng l\u1edbn Argentina. C\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thua 0-3 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn m\u1edf ra v\u1edbi Iceland. M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd m\u1edf toang c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp khi ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t cu\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Iceland tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ed1p c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n 2 nh\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec3u Saudi Arabia v\u00e0 Panama. Vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 nhau \u0111\u00f4i khi l\u1ea1i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ni\u1ec1m vui \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ai \u01b0a th\u00edch d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00fang ta h\u1eb3n s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ea3m v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi thi\u1ebfu c\u1edfi m\u1edf v\u00e0 khan hi\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. 5 trong s\u1ed1 6 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Nigeria \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ed1i \u0111a l\u00e0 2 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi rung. Vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh&rdquo; kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 may m\u1eafn s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nigeria cua Moses dut diem yeu kem\" title=\"Nigeria cua Moses dut diem yeu kem\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Nigeria-cua-Moses-dut-diem-yeu-kem.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m c\u1ee7a Nigeria c\u00f3 c\u00e1i lo l\u1eafng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00ednh ra, trong 6 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 giao h\u1eefu n\u00f3i tr\u00ean, Nigeria ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. Trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00e0n l\u01b0\u1edbt v\u00e0 tranh ch\u1ea5p song ri\u00eang kh\u00e2u d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00ec l\u1ea1i y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1eb3ng n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2u xa, trong tr\u1eadn thua 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y g\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n, Nigeria tung ra t\u1edbi 14 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m song ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 \u0111i tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch. Lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Phi ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt trong vi\u1ec7c ghi b\u00e0n d\u00f9 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p r\u1ed3i qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn sang b\u00ean kia, th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch t\u1eeb l\u00e2u c\u1ee7a Iceland. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n khi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t b\u00e0i treo b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng v\u00e0 d\u00e0i v\u00e0o th\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng chi\u1ec1u cao t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Argentina vs Iceland Finbogason\" title=\"Argentina vs Iceland Finbogason\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Argentina-vs-Iceland-Finbogason.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Phong c\u00e1ch t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Iceland kh\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n \u0111i\u1ec7u</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecnh c\u1edd khi 5 trong s\u1ed1 6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Iceland t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1edf xu\u1ed1ng. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 g\u1ee3i cho ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 y\u00ean t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Iceland s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 2 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi rung.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n quen thu\u1ed9c s\u1ebd l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Volgograd Arena: Nigeria c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng song b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh. C\u00f2n Iceland, h\u1ecd ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh, ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng d\u00f9 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u00f2n ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o may r\u1ee7i. C\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ea7n may m\u1eafn m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1ed1c 2 b\u00e0n m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea quan tr\u1ecdng:</strong><br>\r\n- 5 trong s\u1ed1 6 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Nigeria c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf xu\u1ed1ng<br>\r\n- Trong 6 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean, Nigeria ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n<br>\r\n- 5 trong s\u1ed1 6 tr\u1eadn ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Iceland kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 2 b\u00e0n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>\u00cdt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (t\u1ed1i \u0111a 2 b\u00e0n)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: <strong>H\u00f2a 0-0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<h2>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 con s\u1ed1 3 (O 3)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 5 (O 4 1/2)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Nigeria c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn s\u1ebd nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n (+1/4)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Nigeria hi\u1ec7p 1 s\u1ebd nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n (+1/4)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Nigeria c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn s\u1ebd t\u1eeb 2 tr\u1edf l\u00ean (O 2)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-brazil-vs-costa-rica-463-189267.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/link-xem-brazil-vs-costa-rica.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-brazil-vs-costa-rica-463-189267.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Brazil vs Costa Rica 19h00 ng\u00e0y 22/6 (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Brazil vs Costa Rica: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil vs Costa Rica b\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018 l\u00fac...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-costa-rica-vs-brazil-va-du-doan-soi-keo-brazil-vs-costa-rica-421-189250.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nhan-dinh-costa-rica-vs-brazil-va-du-doan-soi-keo-brazil-vs-costa-rica.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-costa-rica-vs-brazil-va-du-doan-soi-keo-brazil-vs-costa-rica-421-189250.html\">Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng cho c\u1ea7u \u0111inh gi\u1edd \u0111\u1eb9p Costa Rica vs Brazil</span><br>\r\n<span>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Costa Rica vs Brazil bu\u1ed9c ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 nhi\u1ec1u. Brazil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t hay...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-thuy-si-vs-serbia-va-du-doan-soi-keo-serbia-vs-thuy-si-421-189275.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nhan-dinh-thuy-si-vs-serbia-va-du-doan-soi-keo-serbia-vs-thuy-si.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-thuy-si-vs-serbia-va-du-doan-soi-keo-serbia-vs-thuy-si-421-189275.html\">Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u00e1ng ng\u1eddi cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u hot Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 vs Serbia</span><br>\r\n<span>Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 vs Serbia l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng E, n\u01a1i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Brazil. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 vs Serbia c\u1ee7a Bongda24h s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ch\u00fang ta...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ly (TTVN)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"459","checkdouble":"189271"},{"date":"16:25 22/06","title":"12 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a Argentina tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/12-thong-ke-gay-soc-sau-tran-thua-cua-argentina-truoc-croatia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Argentina \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua Croatia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-3, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Argentina vs Croatia.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>1.</strong> Messi ch\u1ec9 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 1 l\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Iceland anh d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn 11 l\u1ea7n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, d\u00f9 1 l\u1ea7n hay 11 l\u1ea7n th\u00ec Messi \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf World Cup 2018.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Argentina vs Croatia - B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Argentina vs Croatia - B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Thong-ke-Argentina-vs-Croatia---Bang-D-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Messi g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>2.</strong> Caballero tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n th\u1ee9 t\u01b0 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, sau David de Gea (T\u00e2y Ban Nha), Wojciech Szczesny (Ba Lan) v\u00e0 Mohammed Al-Owais (Saudi Arabia).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>3. </strong>Trong hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Croatia, Argentina ch\u1ec9 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Iran trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi TBN l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>4. </strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Argentina vs Croatia ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m trong hi\u1ec7p 1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>5. </strong>Messi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 20 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia, th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Sergio Aguero ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>6. </strong>Messi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m c\u1ee7a Croatia trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>7.</strong> Trong 21 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1 v\u00e0 11 \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2 Sergio Aguero th\u1eadm ch\u00ed kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>8.</strong> V\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Argentina, Luka Modric \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a Croatia ghi b\u00e0n trong hai tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf World Cup, sau Davor Suker v\u00e0 Ivan Perisic.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric tiet lo bi quyet danh bai Argentina.\" title=\"Luka Modric ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/luka-modric-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-danh-bai-argentina.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Luka Modric ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>9.</strong> Sau 44 n\u0103m Argentina m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua 2 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u1edf World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>10. </strong>K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1958 \u0111\u1ebfn nay Argentina m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn thua v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 3 b\u00e0n \u1edf World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>11.</strong> \u1ede World Cup 2002, Argentina c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nigeria v\u00e0 Anh, \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. NHM \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 lo l\u1eafng cho t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Albicelestes.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-argentina-03-croatia-421-189274.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-argentina-03-croatia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-argentina-03-croatia-421-189274.html\">4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Argentina 0-3 Croatia</span><br>\r\nArgentina \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua Croatia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-3, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Argentina vs Croatia.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>12.</strong> Luka Modric \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 100% v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng (2), kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn (3) v\u00e0 qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi (3).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"458","checkdouble":"189272"},{"date":"17:23 22/06","title":"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Argentina 0-3 Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-argentina-03-croatia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Argentina \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua Croatia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-3, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Argentina vs Croatia.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Willy Caballero</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSergio Romero d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Willy Caballero tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Argentina. Ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Jorge Sampaoli tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng nh\u01b0ng g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Argentina vs Croatia 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Argentina vs Croatia 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Argentina-vs-Croatia-4-nguoi-tot-nhat-va-3-nguoi-te-nhat-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Willy Caballero m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tha th\u1ee9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n g\u1eb7p Iceland, Caballero ch\u01a1i thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 36 tu\u1ed5i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ra v\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Argentina vs Croatia r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay ng\u00f4i sao 36 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00fat 53, Caballero c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 Ante Rebic ch\u1edbp th\u1eddi c\u01a1 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u1ed1ng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Croatia. Caballero tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n th\u1ee9 t\u01b0 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, sau David de Gea (T\u00e2y Ban Nha), Wojciech Szczesny (Ba Lan) v\u00e0 Mohammed AlOwais (Saudi Arabia).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh sinh n\u0103m 1981 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nigeria.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Croatia</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Croatia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 tung ra 8 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, trong \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 2 \u0111i tr\u00fang khung th\u00e0nh. Argentina d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng n\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c khoa h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a Croatia.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Croatia\" title=\"Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/argentina-lo-sot-vo-voi-phat-bieu-cua-hlv-croatia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Croatia ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua n\u00e0o \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Croatia \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua n\u00e0o, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc ca ro ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 4 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang khung th\u00e0nh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 Vrsaljko, Vida, Lovren v\u00e0 Strinic \u0111ang k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhau c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef c\u1ef1 ly \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh h\u1ee3p l\u00fd v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Brozovic \u0111ang gi\u00fap th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Subasic ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Lionel Messi</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n g\u1eb7p Iceland, Messi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn 11 l\u1ea7n, anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. \u0110\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Croatia \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2, M10 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi Thien tai cung phai gap thoi 1\" title=\"Messi Thi\u00ean t\u00e0i c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p th\u1eddi 1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Thong-ke-Argentina-vs-Croatia---Bang-D-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Messi g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong hi\u1ec7p 1, Messi ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 20 l\u1ea7n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 90 ph\u00fat nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 ch\u1ec9 tung ra duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u song \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. 2 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Iceland v\u00e0 Croatia, Messi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 12 l\u1ea7n, 4 tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c M10 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Argentina \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Luka Modric</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Luka Modric l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Croatia \u1edf World Cup 2018, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric tiet lo bi quyet danh bai Argentina.\" title=\"Luka Modric ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/luka-modric-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-danh-bai-argentina.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Luka Modric th\u0103ng hoa c\u00f9ng Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n g\u1eb7p Nigeria ch\u00ednh Modric ghi m\u1ed9t trong hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap Croatia gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1985 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Argentina \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nModric l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n gi\u00fap Croatia \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0. V\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Argentina, Luka Modric \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a Croatia ghi b\u00e0n trong hai tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf World Cup, sau Davor Suker v\u00e0 Ivan Perisic.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLuka Modric \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 100% v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng (2), kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn (3) v\u00e0 qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi (3). Anh ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng 62 l\u1ea7n, tung ra 42 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n, t\u1ea1o ra 2 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 2 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Modric ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y Croatia h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Jorge Sampaoli</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jorge Sampaoli g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 khu v\u1ef1c Nam M\u1ef9 , theo \u0111\u00f3 \u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap Argentina gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sampaoli mac sai lam nghiem trong\" title=\"Sampaoli m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/argentina-that-bai-khi-sampaoli-lac-me-hon-tran.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sampaoli \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina v\u1eabn tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 h\u00f9ng h\u1ed3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018 r\u1eb1ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Albicelestes v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u00f4ng n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng Argentina th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd c\u00f9ng m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn Sampaoli ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Argentina kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Sampaoli b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u00f4ng n\u00e0y x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n kh\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Cristiano Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi \u0111ang c\u1ea1nh tranh cho danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng 2018. N\u1ebfu coi phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1edf World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u00eau ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00ec CR7 \u0111ang v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi M10.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo va cu nhay tren dinh the gioi\" title=\"Ronaldo v\u00e0 c\u00fa nh\u1ea3y tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Ronaldo-va-cu-nhay-tren-dinh-the-gioi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Messi \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 33 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, anh l\u1eadp hat-trick tr\u01b0\u1edbc TBN v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00fap Seleccao \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ma R\u1ed1c. Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ghi 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n100% s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 B\u0110N c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1edfi Ronaldo, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985 c\u0169ng \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi v\u1edbi 4 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a CR7 gi\u00fap B\u0110N c\u00f3 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Messi ch\u01b0a ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n n\u00e0o sau 12 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, s\u1ef1 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a M10 \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn Argentina \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Iceland ho\u1eb7c Nigeria</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-argentina-vs-croatia-421-189189.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Argentina vs Croatia</span> gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc ca r\u00f4 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u. C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i chia \u0111\u1ec1u cho 3 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. Tr\u1eadn Iceland vs Nigeria quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Nigeria vs Iceland\" title=\"Preview Nigeria vs Iceland\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/nhan-dinh-nigeria-vs-iceland-va-du-doan-iceland-vs-nigeria.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Argentina \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Nigeria ho\u1eb7c Iceland</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Iceland th\u1eafng, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 tr\u1eadn, \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ea3o n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n h\u00f2a Croatia l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Argentina c\u0169ng m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Nigeria, \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. N\u1ebfu &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh&rdquo; \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Iceland, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean BXH.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina, Nigeria s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f9ng Croatia \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u0169ng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi s\u00e1ng c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"457","checkdouble":"189274"},{"date":"17:44 22/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u00e1ng ng\u1eddi cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u hot Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 vs Serbia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/22/nhan-dinh-thuy-si-vs-serbia-va-du-doan-soi-keo-serbia-vs-thuy-si.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 vs Serbia l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng E, n\u01a1i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Brazil. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 vs Serbia c\u1ee7a Bongda24h s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ch\u00fang ta gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c n\u00f3ng b\u1ecfng n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>\u00cdt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (t\u1ed1i \u0111a 2 b\u00e0n)<br>\r\n- <strong>Serbia t\u1eeb h\u00f2a t\u1edbi th\u1eafng</strong><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: <strong>H\u00f2a 0-0 ho\u1eb7c Serbia th\u1eafng 1-0</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1:</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<em>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u:</em> Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 vs Serbia<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1eddi gian:</em> 2h ng\u00e0y 23/6<br>\r\n<em>\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m:</em> S\u00e2n Kaliningrad<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>TLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 -0.96*0:0*0.91 Serbia<br>\r\n<em>TBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>Nhi\u1ec1u -0.89*2*0.83 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 vs Serbia v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, soi k\u00e8o Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 vs Serbia v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, soi k\u00e8o Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/nhan-dinh-thuy-si-vs-serbia-va-du-doan-soi-keo-serbia-vs-thuy-si.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 vs Serbia 1h ng\u00e0y 23/6</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\n\u00cdt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng (U 2)</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ecdng l\u1ea1i trong ch\u00fang ta sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng E l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn n\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng tuy\u1ebfn t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 v\u00e0 Serbia. V\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129, h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng v\u00e0 khoa h\u1ecdc. D\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Vladimir Petkovic, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 khi\u1ebfn Brazil im ti\u1ebfng trong su\u1ed1t g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBrazil nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00ed th\u1ebf v\u00e0 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ph\u00fat 20 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Philippe Coutinho. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 tr\u1edf \u0111i, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Selecao im ti\u1ebfng. B\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch, t\u1eeb si\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t c\u00e1c kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng, ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t t\u1ed1t tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng cho t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1 r\u1eafn, kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Brazil vs Thuy Si Neymar bi pham loi\" title=\"Brazil vs Thuy Si Neymar bi pham loi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/Valon-Behrami-noi-ve-Neymar-sau-tran-Brazil-vs-Thuy-Sy-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 khi\u1ebfn cho Brazil ph\u1ea3i k\u00eau tr\u1eddi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, Serbia c\u00f2n ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o h\u01a1n Th\u1ee5y S\u0129. X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t con ng\u01b0\u1eddi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thu\u1ed9c Nam T\u01b0 c\u0169 c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u h\u01a1n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi tuy\u1ebfn. Ri\u00eang \u1edf h\u1eadu ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng gi\u1eefa kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Kolarov, Ivanovic, Tosic v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Milenkovic.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a h\u1ebft, ngay ph\u00eda tr\u00ean h\u1ecd c\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u1eb7p Matic, Milivojevic c\u00e0n qu\u00e9t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec7t. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Mitrovic v\u00e0 Milinkovic-Savic kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i pressing ngay b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n b\u00ean kia. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ed7 m\u00e1y \u0111\u1ea7y c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica l\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong su\u1ed1t 90 ph\u00fat, d\u00f9 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn hay l\u00f9i s\u00e2u b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, Serbia \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng cho Costa Rica b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n n\u00e0o. Nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m do th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Stojkovic tr\u1ea5n gi\u1eef l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t hi\u1ebfm hoi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ivanovic pha ky luc de tro thanh cau thu ra san nhieu tran nhat cho DT Serbia.\" title=\"Ivanovic ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn nh\u1ea5t cho \u0110T Serbia.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/Nhan-dinh-Serbia-vs-Thuy-Si-(1h-ngay-236)-Dai-bang-lai-bay-ca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u01b0ng Serbia c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng cho nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 vs Serbia. Hai h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u1eddng. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n thua t\u1edbi t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u m\u1ed7i khi b\u01b0\u1edbc ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 World Cup 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 v\u00e0 Serbia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 th\u1ee9 2 sau Brazil \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. V\u1edbi t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Kaliningrad, s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean cao ng\u1ea5t. V\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 vs Serbia s\u1ebd \u00edt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng (2 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf xu\u1ed1ng) l\u00e0 s\u00e1ng su\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ch\u1ecdn:</strong> \u00cdt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng (U 2)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Serbia t\u1eeb h\u00f2a t\u1edbi th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ee5y S\u0129 v\u00e0 Serbia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ngang t\u00e0i ngang s\u1ee9c \u1edf m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, Serbia c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tuy\u1ebfn. X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng&rdquo; bi\u1ebfn h\u00f3a h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee5y S\u0129 nh\u01b0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 Brazil ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng cho Xherdan Shaqiri v\u00e0 ch\u1edd nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t khi Shaqiri \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u0103m s\u00f3c k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 x\u1ea3y ra tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c b\u1ebf t\u1eafc. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Serbia thang Thuy Si\" title=\"Serbia thang Thuy Si\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Serbia-thang-Thuy-Si.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Serbia c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u01a1n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil kh\u00f3 l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i th\u1eadm tr\u00ed ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i. Serbia s\u1edf h\u1eefu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 Tosic, Ivanovic, Milenkovic, Matic, Milinkovi\u0107-Savic r\u1ed3i Mitrovic&hellip;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng Serbia kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn. Khi c\u1ea7n, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3ng ng\u1eafn v\u1edbi k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00fat \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea7m xa v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch Kolarov s\u00fat &ldquo;ch\u00e1y l\u01b0\u1edbi&rdquo; Costa Rica.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110a d\u1ea1ng trong t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 v\u00e0 Serbia. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c m\u0169i c\u00f4ng Serbia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ch\u1ecdn:</strong> Serbia<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>\u00cdt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (t\u1ed1i \u0111a 2 b\u00e0n)<br>\r\n- <strong>Serbia t\u1eeb h\u00f2a t\u1edbi th\u1eafng</strong><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: <strong>H\u00f2a 0-0 ho\u1eb7c Serbia th\u1eafng 1-0</strong></div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u ghi b\u00e0n<br>\r\n- Qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Serbia<br>\r\n- Qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Serbia<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Serbia trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng thua (+1/2)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Serbia trong hi\u1ec7p 1 kh\u00f4ng thua (+1/4)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Serbia trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 5 (O 4 1/2)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 t\u1eeb 5 tr\u1edf l\u00ean (O 4 1/2)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb 3 tr\u1edf l\u00ean (O 3)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Serbia trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 2 (O 1 1/2)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-nigeria-vs-iceland-va-du-doan-iceland-vs-nigeria-421-189271.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nhan-dinh-nigeria-vs-iceland-va-du-doan-iceland-vs-nigeria.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-nigeria-vs-iceland-va-du-doan-iceland-vs-nigeria-421-189271.html\">Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ea3m cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Nigeria vs Iceland</span><br>\r\n<span>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Iceland \u0111ang n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018. V\u00e0 m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m, ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c mang...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-costa-rica-vs-brazil-va-du-doan-soi-keo-brazil-vs-costa-rica-421-189250.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/link-xem-brazil-vs-costa-rica.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-costa-rica-vs-brazil-va-du-doan-soi-keo-brazil-vs-costa-rica-421-189250.html\">Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng cho c\u1ea7u \u0111inh gi\u1edd \u0111\u1eb9p Costa Rica vs Brazil</span><br>\r\n<span>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Costa Rica vs Brazil bu\u1ed9c ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 nhi\u1ec1u. Brazil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t hay...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ly (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"456","checkdouble":"189275"},{"date":"10:51 22/06","title":"Chelsea c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/21/chelsea-co-tan-binh-dau-tien-voi-gia-31-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua trung v\u1ec7 Daniele Rugani</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Rudiger t\u1eeb Roma v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge c\u0169ng g\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i trung v\u1ec7 Andreas Christensen. S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u1ea5p v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng do John Terry \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/21/chelsea-co-tan-binh-dau-tien-voi-gia-31-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu trong tay kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trung v\u1ec7 nh\u01b0ng Chelsea v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGary Cahill \u0111\u00e3 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong khi \u0111\u00f3 David Luiz mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 bu\u1ed9c Chelsea ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p\u00a0h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea quan t\u00e2m trung v\u1ec7 Daniele Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Juventus.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chi-354-trieu-bang-mua-hau-ve-juventus-172-175920.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Rugani</span>, song Chelsea t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Daniele Rugani</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Sarri s\u1eafp ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Chelsea thay Conte, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Daniele Rugani. V\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 58 tu\u1ed5i b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch ph\u1ea3i mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Rugani cua Juventus\" title=\"trung ve Rugani cua Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/21/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-ngay-2112-Arsenal-chi-dam-tranh-hang-voi-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Rugani v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Italia \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Juventus b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi Chelsea s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 vi\u1ec7c Sarri ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thay Conte, sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 lu\u00f4n b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng Daniele Rugani t\u1eeb Juventus. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"455","checkdouble":"189240"},{"date":"10:09 22/06","title":"\u0110T Ph\u00e1p to\u00e0n th\u1eafng: \u0110i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng trong c\u01a1n b\u0129 c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/dt-phap-toan-thang-diem-sang-trong-con-bi-cuc-cua-cac-ong-lon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao trong danh s\u00e1ch \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng World Cup 2018, song c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Ph\u00e1p ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u2018\u00f4ng l\u1edbn\u2019 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</h2><br>\r\n<h2>\u0110i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebf th\u1eeba c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n EURO 2016 hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. H\u1ecd \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1ebb \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra, Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ed1 4 trong danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup n\u0103m nay theo t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u00e1i Dabble Bet \u0111\u01b0a ra. H\u1ecd x\u1ebfp sau Brazil, \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Tuy nhi\u00ean khi m\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u1ea7m l\u0169i ti\u1ebfn b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Ph\u00e1p to\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0110i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng trong c\u01a1n b\u0129 c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Ph\u00e1p to\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0110i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng trong c\u01a1n b\u0129 c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/DT-Phap-toan-thang-Diem-sang-trong-con-bi-cuc-cua-cac-ong-lon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Kylian Mbappe m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110T Ph\u00e1p vs Peru.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0110\u1ee9c, Argentina \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft m\u00f9i b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n T\u00e2y Ban Nha, B\u0110N hay Brazil \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a th\u00ec Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp sau hai tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C. Hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dac v\u00e0 Peru d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t \u00edt \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu trong k\u1ef3 World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 trong ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00f4m qua, truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi t\u1eadp trung n\u00f3i nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn thua th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a Argentina tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta qu\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp t\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn trong t\u01b0 duy chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p \u0110T \u00dac.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">So v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n b\u1ecb ch\u00ea l\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ee9c, \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y HLV Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh khi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 4-2-3-1 thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 4-3-3 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. Giroud v\u00e0o s\u00e2n ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u thay cho Ousmane Dembele, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Antoine Griezmann v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, Corentin Tolisso - ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 l\u1ec7ch t\u00f4ng v\u1edbi hai \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Paul Pogba v\u00e0 N&rsquo;Golo Kante c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Blaise Matuidi&nbsp;m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Ch\u00ednh hai s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt t\u00e1o b\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p thi \u0111\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Deschamps thay doi chien thuat, dat niem tin vao Giroud\" title=\"Deschamps thay \u0111\u1ed5i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Giroud\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/chipu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Deschamps ghi d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n b\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Giroud</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 c\u01a1 b\u1eafp c\u1ee7a Matuidi ch\u1ebfch b\u00ean ph\u00eda c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m t\u01b0\u1eddng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Giroud \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i Peru, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3, c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t kh\u00e1t khao gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nu\u00f4i tham v\u1ecdng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup. \u0110\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i khi Peru b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng s\u01a1 h\u1edf, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 tung ra nh\u1eefng &lsquo;mi\u1ebfng \u0111\u00e1nh&rsquo; \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1eady.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y b\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a HLV Deschamps khi tung nh\u1eefng &lsquo;qu\u00e2n c\u1edd d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c&rsquo; v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay cho nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t l\u00fac n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 g\u1ea1c l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c &lsquo;\u00f4ng l\u1edbn&rsquo; v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf sau nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i v\u1eeba qua t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup</span>.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i World Cup n\u0103m nay s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0110T \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. V\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng C s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Les Bleus tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D l\u00e0 Croatia. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng D c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 Iceland, Argentina ho\u1eb7c Nigeria.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 1 trong 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ph\u00e1p. N\u1ebfu v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng 1/8, \u0110T&nbsp;Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1eafng trong c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng A v\u00e0 nh\u00ec B t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Phap 2-1 Australia\" title=\"Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Thay-gi-sau-man-ra-quan-cua-cac-ung-vien-vo-dich-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Ph\u00e1p ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng A, c\u1ea3 Nga v\u00e0 Uruguay \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9ng t\u1ea7m v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p trong khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng B nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. V\u00ec th\u1ebf ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u00fang s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c n\u1eb1m trong tay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sao \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u00f2n l\u00fac n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng C c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. M\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Didier Deschamps l\u00e2m v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3. Do v\u1eady, h\u1ecd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 quan \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-phap-vs-peru-461-189190.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/pha-luoi-peru-kylian-mbappe-lap-ky-luc-trong-lich-su-dt-phap.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-phap-vs-peru-461-189190.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 1-0 Peru (B\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o lam gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp ch\u1ec9 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018. Trong khi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1ea1m...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-phap-vs-peru-463-189178.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/ket-qua-phap-vs-peru.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-phap-vs-peru-463-189178.html\">Ph\u00e1p 1-0 Peru (KT): Gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n, Les Bleus ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Ph\u00e1p vs Peru: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs Peru b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 22h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-an-tuong-trong-ngay-phap-loai-peru-khoi-world-cup-2018-465-189196.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nhung-hinh-anh-an-tuong-trong-ngay-phap-loai-peru-khoi-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-an-tuong-trong-ngay-phap-loai-peru-khoi-world-cup-2018-465-189196.html\">Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong ng\u00e0y Ph\u00e1p lo\u1ea1i Peru kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u01b0ng tr\u00e1i tim c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Nam M\u1ef9 khi \u0110T Peru b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p>Minh Long (TTVN)</o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"454","checkdouble":"189241"},{"date":"10:56 22/06","title":"Hazard c\u00f2n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea th\u00ec \u0111\u1eebng m\u01a1 Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/11/mo-ve-qua-bong-vang-hazard-nen-roi-bo-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Li\u1ec7t k\u00ea th\u1eed xem nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u0103m nay n\u00e0o! Argentina c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo, Ai C\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah, Anh c\u1ee7a Harry Kane, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a Son Heung-min, Ba Lan c\u1ee7a Robert Lewandowski. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Christian Eriksen.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">May m\u1eafn song h\u00e0nh &quot;k\u1ebb ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n&quot; \u0110an M\u1ea1ch...</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 gian nan v\u00e0 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u1eabn l\u00e0m sao t\u00ecm ra l\u1ed1i tho\u00e1t \u0111\u1ebfn Nga m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Sau ba tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n B\u1eafc \u00c2u th\u1eafng Armenia t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 thua Ba Lan r\u1ed3i Montenegro, x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 t\u01b0 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 su\u1ea5t play-off cho \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t nh\u00ec.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam 17 trong t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 21 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1i \u0111a v\u00e0 h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t CH Ireland v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-1 ngay tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t kh\u00e1ch trong tr\u1eadn play-off l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Age Hareide b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a FIFA su\u1ed1t t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng M\u01b0\u1eddi 2016.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia Eriksen t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia Eriksen t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Dan-Mach-1-1-Australia-Eriksen-toa-sang-trong-doi-hinh-phan-dien-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u00fa hat-trick c\u1ee7a Christian Eriksen \u0111\u01b0a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ki\u1ec3u g\u00ec c\u0169ng t\u00ecm ra l\u1ed1i tho\u00e1t, \u0111\u00f3 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch trong g\u1ea7n hai n\u0103m qua. \u0110\u01a1n c\u1eed nh\u01b0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Peru ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018, ai c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 may m\u1eafn nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o khi kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u1ee9 \u0111\u1eebng n\u00f3i g\u00ec t\u1eeb h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ebfn thua, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kasper Schmeichel \u0111\u00e3 \u0111o\u00e1n sai h\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;Peru x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f4i khi n\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1eady. May m\u1eafn ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.&rdquo; &ndash; V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn nh\u01b0 HLV 65 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Na Uy, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Hareide c\u0169ng s\u1ebd n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 sau tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-dan-mach-vs-australia-463-189157.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia</span>.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-dan-mach-vs-australia-463-189157.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/ket-qua-dan-mach-vs-australia.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-dan-mach-vs-australia-463-189157.html\">\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia (KT): L\u00ednh ch\u00ec v\u00e0 Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai b\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 l\u00fac...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00eau ca v\u1ec1 hai qu\u1ea3 penalty ph\u1ea1t h\u1ecd trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 may m\u1eafn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng trong th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 n\u00e0y. Ch\u1eb3ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n B\u1eafc \u00c2u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 k\u00e9m c\u01a1 so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ea1i D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ee7 may \u0111\u1ec3 tho\u00e1t thua qu\u1ea3 penalty ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a chuy\u00ean gia Mile Jedinak, \u1ea5y v\u1eady \u0110an M\u1ea1ch xem ra v\u1eabn c\u00f2n may ch\u00e1n khi kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dac l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Australia s\u00fat 13 so v\u1edbi 8 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, d\u1eabn 5-3 \u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng. Nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean r\u1ed3i, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch &ldquo;ki\u1ec3u g\u00ec c\u0169ng t\u00ecm ra l\u1ed1i tho\u00e1t&rdquo; v\u00e0 gi\u1edd, h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Christian Eriksen \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i anh! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Christian Eriksen \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i anh! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Christian-Eriksen-Dan-Mach-co-the-dong-vai-phan-dien,-khong-phai-anh!-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Christian Eriksen ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">... nh\u01b0ng Christian Eriksen th\u00ec x\u1ee9ng d\u00e1ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh h\u00f9ng</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Christian Eriksen l\u00e0 h\u1ea1t nh\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng y\u1ebfu g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch trong \u00edt n\u0103m qua, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n tham d\u1ef1 World Cup ch\u1ec9 sau hai n\u0103m b\u1ecb Albania \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i v\u00e0 ch\u1ea7u r\u00eca Euro 2016 v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng cho 24 anh t\u00e0i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng n\u00f3i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y h\u01a1n c\u1ea3, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c Eriksen t\u1ef1 l\u00e0m m\u1edbi, th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n l\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi \u1edf khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf. Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Tottenham, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 26 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o thu\u1ea7n t\u00fay, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec Premier League \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Hai n\u0103m qua, ch\u1ec9 duy nh\u1ea5t Kevin De Bruyne c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n anh (209 vs 207).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 Spurs v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t Harry Kane s\u00fat b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n nh\u01b0 c\u01a1m b\u1eefa, Eriksen \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m lu\u00f4n vai tr\u00f2 ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t sau khi &ldquo;danh h\u00e0i&rdquo; Lord Nicklas Bendtner kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng bay \u0111\u1ebfn Nga v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc. Trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec sau Eriksen l\u00e0 Nicolai Jorgensen v\u1edbi 8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia Eriksen t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia Eriksen t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/100907-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Christian Eriksen t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t chu\u1ed7i 9 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i, Eriksen ghi 10 b\u00e0n, chi\u1ebfm 40% chi\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. C\u00fa volley ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p tung n\u00f3c l\u01b0\u1edbi Australia mang v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 11 trong 11 tr\u1eadn qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a anh trong 44 tr\u1eadn Premier League g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Christian Eriksen &ndash; c\u00e2y s\u0103n b\u00e0n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc th\u1ee9 9 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, 26 tu\u1ed5i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u1ea7n n\u00ean bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng di\u1ec5n ra su\u00f4n s\u1ebb nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Th\u00e1ng M\u01b0\u1eddi 2014, HLV Morten Olsen th\u1eddi b\u1ea5y gi\u1edd ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Eriksen qu\u00e1 th\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed9ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG. Ng\u00f4i sao Tottenham ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy ho\u1ea1ch cho ch\u1ee9c th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n anh \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u00e1 t\u00ednh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh tinh th\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 ch\u00ednh Hugo Lloris, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf Spurs, Eriksen thu\u1ed9c tu\u00fdp ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ea7m l\u1eb7ng, n\u00f3i \u00edt l\u00e0m nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eafm vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 tr\u1ecf, h\u00f2 h\u00e9t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia Eriksen t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia Eriksen t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/102431-13.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Christian Eriksen t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 y\u00ean b\u00ecnh, c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ed5 t\u00edch nh\u00e2n v\u0103n n\u00ean t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean k\u00e9o theo, \u0110TQG c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00f3ng vai ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n. T\u1ef1a nh\u01b0 bi\u1ec7t danh &ldquo;nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa l\u00ednh ch\u00ec&rdquo; b\u00ecnh d\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Euro 1992 c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c d\u00e2n. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru v\u00e0 Australia ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eeba m\u1eaft gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u1eabu v\u1eady, r\u1ed3i anh c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o s\u1edf h\u1eefu Christian Eriksen \u0111\u00e2u. \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111i xa tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng n\u1ebfu Ph\u00e1p nghi\u00eam t\u00fac c\u00f2n \u00dac l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru. C\u01a1 m\u00e0 nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n kh\u00e1c \u1edf World Cup, lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng mi\u1ec5n nhi\u1ec5m v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Christian Eriksen, nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng, v\u1ecb anh h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u0110an M\u1ea1ch &ldquo;ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/christian-eriksen-tuyen-bo-ghet-var-sau-tran-hoa-cua-dan-mach-465-189199.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/christian-eriksen-tuyen-bo-ghet-var-sau-tran-hoa-cua-dan-mach.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/christian-eriksen-tuyen-bo-ghet-var-sau-tran-hoa-cua-dan-mach-465-189199.html\">Christian Eriksen tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 gh\u00e9t VAR sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch</span><br>\r\nC\u00f9ng v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Kasper Schmeichel, Christian Eriksen tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 gh\u00e9t VAR khi c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn \u0110T \u0110an M\u1ea1ch b\u1ecb th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua t\u1ea1i World...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"453","checkdouble":"189242"},{"date":"10:31 22/06","title":"Pogba ca ng\u1ee3i Kante sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/pogba-ca-ngoi-kante-sau-tran-thang-truoc-peru.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a N\u2019Golo Kante, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i \u0110TQG Ph\u00e1p.\r\n\r\n</h2><span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\" style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Pogba ca ng\u1ee3i Kante sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif;\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 21/6 (gi\u1edd Nga), \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Kylian Mbappe l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi&nbsp;ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Ph\u00e1p \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t, ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i t\u1edbi N&rsquo;Golo Kante, &lsquo;m\u00e1y qu\u00e9t&rsquo; khu trung tuy\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba cung dong doi Phap an mung ban thang\" title=\"Pogba cung dong doi Phap an mung ban thang\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/pogba-ca-ngoi-kante-sau-tran-thang-truoc-peru.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Pogba v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 hay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pogba th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. &ldquo;\u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi N'Golo Kante, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 tr\u1edf n\u00ean d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1ea1y kh\u1eafp s\u00e2n m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft m\u1ec7t. C\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Kante c\u00f3 15 l\u00e1 ph\u1ed5i v\u1eady. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c thi \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf.&nbsp; \u0110T Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 to\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. B\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5y, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 b\u1ea5t t\u1eadn, Kante \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n, thu h\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao c\u1ee7a Kante c\u0169ng gi\u00fap c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a anh nh\u01b0 Pogba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i d\u00e2ng cao h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa \u0110T Ph\u00e1p thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n ti\u1ec1m \u1ea9n s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, \u0110T Ph\u00e1p c\u1ee7a Pogba s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng \u0110an M\u1ea1nh. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m, Les Bleus s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. Do \u0111\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea7m ch\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef s\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out sau \u0111\u00f3.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-phap-toan-thang-diem-sang-trong-con-bi-cuc-cua-cac-ong-lon-421-189241.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/dt-phap-toan-thang-diem-sang-trong-con-bi-cuc-cua-cac-ong-lon.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-phap-toan-thang-diem-sang-trong-con-bi-cuc-cua-cac-ong-lon-421-189241.html\">\u0110T Ph\u00e1p to\u00e0n th\u1eafng: \u0110i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng trong c\u01a1n b\u0129 c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn</span><br />\r\nKh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao trong danh s\u00e1ch \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng World Cup 2018, song c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Ph\u00e1p ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 &lsquo;\u00f4ng l\u1edbn&rsquo; c\u00f3 m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/pha-luoi-peru-kylian-mbappe-lap-ky-luc-trong-lich-su-dt-phap-465-189192.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/pha-luoi-peru-kylian-mbappe-lap-ky-luc-trong-lich-su-dt-phap.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/pha-luoi-peru-kylian-mbappe-lap-ky-luc-trong-lich-su-dt-phap-465-189192.html\">Ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Peru, Kylian Mbappe l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</span><br />\r\nV\u1edbi pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng duy nh\u1ea5t gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Peru, Kylian Mbappe l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t ghi b\u00e0n cho \u0110T Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn c\u1ea5p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-phap-vs-peru-461-189190.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/pha-luoi-peru-kylian-mbappe-lap-ky-luc-trong-lich-su-dt-phap.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-phap-vs-peru-461-189190.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 1-0 Peru (B\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018)</span><br />\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o lam gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp ch\u1ec9 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018. Trong khi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1ea1m...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"452","checkdouble":"189243"},{"date":"10:21 22/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 22/6 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nhan-dinh-thanh-hoa-vs-binh-duong-17h00-ngay-226-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thanh H\u00f3a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 22/6 (V\u00f2ng 15 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 226 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 226 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Thanh-Hoa-vs-Binh-Duong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Thanh H\u00f3a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Thanh H\u00f3a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng: 2-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 nguy c\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u0103ng b\u1eb1ng sau nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u1ea3y ch\u00e2n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c v\u1edbi B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thu\u1ed9c nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i SLNA, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Tr\u1ea7n Minh Chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-2. \u0110\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 4 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i V-League 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 sa s\u00fat v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t Th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t th\u1ee9 v\u0169 kh\u00ed tinh th\u1ea7n. \u1ede ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00f3, chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn x\u1ee9 Thanh ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2&nbsp;HLV Tr\u1ea7n Minh Chi\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n, Thanh H\u00f3a l\u1ea1i \u0111ang d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00fang qu\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ea1o sau nh\u1eefng l\u00f9m x\u00f9m n\u01a1i h\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 1-0 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t m\u1ea1ch 4 tr\u1eadn ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1&nbsp; \u0111i\u1ec3m, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ca kh\u00fac kh\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n 1-0 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbt nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i, bao g\u1ed3m tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i m\u00f9a n\u00e0y (3-3). Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. N\u00ean nh\u1edb, so v\u1edbi B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, Thanh H\u00f3a s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn cao h\u01a1n. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 h\u1ecd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 v\u1eeba qua, 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 Thanh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 17 tr\u1eadn, Thanh H\u00f3a th\u1eafng 6, h\u00f2a 5, thua 6.<br>\r\n- Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Thanh H\u00f3a, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 th\u1eafng 4, h\u00f2a 3, thua 1. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\nThanh H\u00f3a: B\u1eedu Ng\u1ecdc; \u0110\u00ecnh \u0110\u1ed3ng, Xu\u00e2n H\u01b0ng, Minh T\u00f9ng, V\u0103n Nam, Ho\u00e0ng Th\u1ecbnh, H\u1eefu D\u0169ng, V\u0103n Hi\u1ebfu, Minh Tu\u1ea5n, Tr\u1ecdng Ho\u00e0ng, Ofere.<br>\r\nB\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng: T\u1ea5n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng; Thanh Th\u1ea3o, T\u1ea5n T\u00e0i, Ng\u1ecdc M\u1ea1nh, Hu\u1ef3nh Ph\u00fa, Tr\u1ecdng Huy, V\u0103n V\u0169, D\u0169 \u0110\u1ea1t, Ho\u00e0ng Max, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, Romario.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"451","checkdouble":"189244"}]}